data.name: messageTb.Text
data.value:
Dear {name},
We are pleased to thank you for your enthusiastic participation in our recent technical event, held on 22nd July 2025. Your engagement and contributions played a significant role in making the event a resounding success.
As a token of our appreciation, we are delighted to attach your Certificate of Participation to this email. We hope this certificate serves as a recognition of your dedication and commitment to advancing technical knowledge and community engagement.
If you have any questions or require further information, please feel free to reach out.
Thank you once again for being a valued part of our event. We look forward to your participation in future programs.
Best regards
